epsontmt20iv (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaged release.
  * CUPS raster filter (rastertotmt20iv) rendering pages to ePOS <image> strips.
  * CUPS backend (epos) POSTing jobs to the printer over HTTPS, reporting
    paper-out/cover-open to CUPS and retrying so jobs survive a paper reload.
  * PPD for the 80 mm roll (576 dots @ 203 dpi).

 -- Valper Soluciones y Mantenimientos S.L. <soporte.externos@valpersoluciones.com>  Wed, 22 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0100
